Key Author:  ATRisco

Original Key Author:  MDS31781

This is a new Volume of de_alamo!!!

Features:
- New Textures
- All bugs Fixed
- More ambience
- More Hide Spots
- 2 Bomb Spots

This is de_alamo-atr_v3 a new Edition of de_alamo.
I loved to play on de_alamo, so i decided to add some more stuff, to make the gameplay more exciting...
WARNING... my edition is not based on a film of alamo or something else. 
Please leave me some feedback... so i could change some stuff or fix any errors.
IMPORTANT... i prefer good feedback! :P
Have a lot of fun! :D
